<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<subsection xml:id="aa-section-turntable-subsection-all" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Putting everything together for the turntable</title>

  <p>
    Given that <m>\vec{\Omega} = \Omega \, \hat{k}</m>,
    we can find <m>\vec{\Omega} \times \hat{i}</m>,
    <m>\vec{\Omega} \times \hat{j}</m>,
    and <m>\vec{\Omega} \times \hat{k}</m>
    and verify they match the results of
    <xref ref="eqn-total-derivative-i-final-turntable" text="type-global" />,
    <xref ref="eqn-total-derivative-j-final-turntable" text="type-global" />,
    and <xref ref="eqn-total-derivative-k-final-turntable" text="type-global" />,
    respectively.
  </p>

  <p>
    <md number="yes">
        \vec{\Omega} \times \hat{i}
        =
        \Omega \, \hat{j}
        =
        \frac{D \hat{i}}{Dt}
    </md>
  </p>

  <p>
    <md number="yes">
        \vec{\Omega} \times \hat{j}
        =
        -\Omega \, \hat{i}
        =
        \frac{D \hat{j}}{Dt}
    </md>
  </p>

  <p>
    <md number="yes">
        \vec{\Omega} \times \hat{k}
        =
        \vec{0}
        =
        \frac{D \hat{k}}{Dt}
    </md>
  </p>

  <p>
    Therefore, the derivation is complete.
  </p>

</subsection>